_sText:
So, I’ve gone ahead and ported almost every single map that’s ever been in the Classic Offensive mod into Counter-Strike: Source. That’s right—all the layouts, all the nostalgia, now running in Source! If you’ve ever wondered what these maps would feel like in CS:S, now’s your chance to try them out.

I’ve showcased the maps in the video below, so check it out!
